        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Actually it has nothing to do with HP items.</P><P>When you hit the zoneline you don't zone right away - you stay in the game for anywhere from 10-40 seconds - the server registers all the dmg mobs are doing to you at this time - if you die before you 'poof' then the server thinks you are dead - IF you are dead when you zone the server will strip all your buffs and give you some life back - sometimes it will send you to the safe point in the zone.</P><P>This is not a 'bug' so much as a 'feature' because of the way zones work - this is just a way to make sure you *can't* zone dead.</P><P>- CK<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
