         In situations where you have raid buffs on, the areas where you actually could make it to the zone are pretty slim. It can be annoying solo, but for the solo necro it costs you Shield of the Magi and DMF for the most part. Now for the soloing shammy on the other hand, it is a royal pain in the ass. I have encountered this more then a few times recently, and let me tell you it sucks zoneing pretty low on health and then having to refresh a dozen buffs.</P><P>Cheers,<BR>Ancagalon the Black<BR>Warlock - Terris Thule</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
